::Rex::

The anti-sound feilds block out Gangon's screams, Rex calmly standing near 
the wall. He frowns as he sees Gangon jumping into the wall, walking forward 
and disabling the anti-sound sistem on his cell.

"What's wrong?" Rex asks him, his gun ready.
